data.description: CHARMING HOME ON A CORNER LOT - This property is a must see if your looking for a home in the heart of Los Fresnos. This home features an open floor plan, 3 bedrooms, 1 bath and a easy access laundry area. The sgl car garage was converted into the current living area, but can be used for many other purposes, including a 4th bedroom or office. Outside...you will find a cozy front porch to sit back and relax on after a long days work and in the backyard you will find a large raised deck and a perfect spot for those weekend cook outs and family gatherings.
